data.description: Location! Location! By DHR, Shopping, Restaurants and Quick Access to HWY 281! This 4 Bedrooms/ 3.5 bath PLUS OFFICE offers a Fresh Concept Design with Natural Lighting Throughout, the Island Kitchen is Amazing and Spacious yet Not Exposed At the Entry Door!  Quartz Countertops, Lots of Cabinet Space, and New Samsung Appliances! Split Bedroom Plan with A Perfect Guest Room w/ Private Bathroom & Masters Is A GEM! Spacious Masters and Bathroom with Garden Tub, Separate Shower, Double Sink, Vanity, and Walk-In Closet! High Ceilings, 8'ft Doors, Porcelain Wood Tile Throughout, Energy Efficient Foam Insulation Walls, and Attic! Also, Has a Water Carbon Filtering and Water Softener System Plus A Tankless Water Heater.  Ohhh  the Custom Zebra Blinds Throughout Allow You To Enjoy Natural Lighting in Various Settings. Covered Patio, Sprinkler System, Concrete Paver Entry With So MUCH More!! Sellers added So Many Upgrades It's The Best Bang For Your Buck!   Don't Miss Your Chance! Mask Required
